  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Doodle Harmony is a beautiful Point and Click game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 pairs of doodles are waiting for you to match them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606760/extras/ca0e5a5224eb722cdf4511dbdfaac1c2.poster.avif?t=1726776798\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606760/extras/ca0e5a5224eb722cdf4511dbdfaac1c2.webm?t=1726776798\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2606760/extras/ca0e5a5224eb722cdf4511dbdfaac1c2.mp4?t=1726776798\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Relax with a spectacular original soundtrack!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Found 2 matching ones? Drag them to their counterpart.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧑🏻‍🤝‍🧑🏻 1 Level, 100 pairs of doodles</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♾️ Procedural Level Generation</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎶 Radio System to choose your music</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⏰ Timer Mode with leaderboards</p>",
